Thaumiel WHAT!?


03 Jun 2014 18:18






Thaumielhumanoid.

Wondermainlist...


People who encouraged me to work in this include Crayne, Kalinin and Vlank. Thanks again for telling me this could make it and giving me so much help.

Also thanks to SoullessSingularity, Weizhong, TwistedGears, AndarielHalo and Tagliafierro for their corresponding feedback and patience. : )




Now then. I know this concept (and how I've handled it), is not conventional. How it's risky, too long, too technical and perhaps too boring. However, life consists on taking risks and my internal image of Foundation business is technical, practical, calm and boring; so what the hell, let's post this.

Both the Archive logo and the memetic agent were made by me. I hope they do not feel too out of place. In any case, please leave feedback, be it pleasingly positive or destructively negative.

Also, it was a pleasure to know you all. Edit: I liked the idea and I knew I wasn't alone, but really, this is beyond what I expected. Thanks for your support, people! I'm very glad you liked it! :_D

Authorshipdisclaimer!

'Causeapparently.




This is a translation and a rewrite of SCP-ES-026, Sauelsuesor, written by Dr Reach. Yes, by the same author. Have to be thorough with legal stuff.








